Can I recover partially rendered movies?\
\

\f1\b0 Yes, but it's a little tricky. First and most importantly, 
\f2\i don't quit Crimson FX.
\f1\i0  All temporary files are deleted when Crimson FX quits, so once you quit the program, you will no longer be able to recover aborted or cancelled partial renders.\
\
If you navigate to 
\f3 /tmp
